text: Joona Kangas (born 28 April 1997) is a Finnish freestyle skier. He competed in the 2015 and 2017 FIS Freestyle World Ski Championships, and in the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish male freestyle skiers Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of Finland Category:Freestyle skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics
